Say hello to <b>Stephen</b>,our newest Citizen of the Week! <br><br>Stephen was discovered on the basketball court where he took home a shiny Sink Three Master Trophy. He was a little out of breath from the game, but we managed to get some vital stats for his model-citizen profile, just the same. <br><br>Stephen's been living at <a href="http://millsberry.com/home/?user=sgssports44"><a href='/home/?user=sgssports44'>80259-C Capital Avenue</a>, in Lakeview</a>, since March 18, 2009. He loves the neighborhood and finds the views of the lake very soothing. It's no surprise to learn that Stephen's an avid sportsman&mdash;he's already won about seven trophies in the short span of two months. And, with a bedroom decorated in baseball wallpaper, he doesn't lose a minute of inspiration! <br><br>Stephen's home impresses for the unique way it's designed: simple, organized, and color-coordinated. And, with a hot tub, and a pool with its own diving board, it's clear that Stephen knows how to relax after a heated game of soccer&mdash;or baseball or basketball!<br><br>So, if you need an extra player on your team, just ask our stellar citizen...as long as you don't mind him blasting his favorite country tunes during warm-up! </div>
